TCW Convertible Securities Fund Incsaid it has sold 20 mln shares of its common stock to a groupof underwriters led by Bear Stearns and Co Inc, E.F. Hutton andCo, Advest Inc, Blunt Ellis and Loewi Inc, Piper, Jaffray andHopwook Inc and Sutro and Co Inc.    The shares were sold by the underwriters at ten dlrs pershare in a public offering.    The offering produced net proceeds of 186 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;